
Strings



Useful String Methods

.equals() = compares one string with another to see if they are the same(alternative to '==')
.startsWith() = returns the first letter in a string.
.endsWith() = returns the last letter in a string.
.length() = returns the number of characters in a string.
.indexOf() = returns the first occurrence of whatever character is passed in.
.replace() = replaces one or more characters with whatever is passed in.
.toLowerCase() = changes any uppercase characters in string to lowercase.
.toUppercase() = changes any uppercase characters in string to uppercase.
.trim() = removes any whitespace at the beginning or end of a string.



